# Kotlin Playground Plugin API

This document describes the API of the Kotlin Playground Plugin for Dokka.

## Classes

### KotlinPlaygroundPlugin

Main plugin class that registers the playground functionality.

**Package:** `org.jetbrains.dokka.kotlinplayground`

### KotlinPlaygroundConfiguration

Configuration data class for the plugin.

**Package:** `org.jetbrains.dokka.kotlinplayground`

**Properties:**
- `playgroundScript: String?` - URL to the Kotlin Playground script (optional)
- `playgroundServerUrl: String?` - Base URL for the playground server (optional)

### PlaygroundSamplesTransformer

Internal transformer that processes sample code blocks to make them runnable.

**Package:** `org.jetbrains.dokka.kotlinplayground`

**Note:** This class is internal and should not be used directly.

## Constants

### DEFAULT_KOTLIN_PLAYGROUND_SCRIPT

The default URL for the Kotlin Playground script.

**Value:** `"https://unpkg.com/kotlin-playground@1/dist/playground.min.js"`